  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study : 1ï¼‰to determine whether hydrocortisone is effective in the
      treatment of septic shock and 2) to identify the role of timing of low dose hydrocortisone
      administration in septic shock patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
